JustHireMe Alternance
=====================

This repository is a fork of JustHireMe (https://github.com/vasu-devs/justhireme)
by Adnane Saber for the purpose of building a server-deployable alternance
(mandatory internship) job matching system.

Modifications include:
- Education Matcher module (Mon Master API integration)
- French alternance-specific source adapters
- Generation customization for alternance framing
- Dockerfile and Docker Compose for server deployment
- Pipeline gating: program approval required before resume generation

